title: Hour 1 - Donovan Mitchell, CFP Expansion

description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, Dan dissects the contractual complexities that come with a college football playoff expansion.  Plus, discussions on airdropping naked photos to strangers and awkward life talks with parents.
